# Design System Rules: Kulik Oleg Style (Ours Mini Program)

## 1. Token Definitions
Design tokens are centralized in `src/styles/theme.scss`. All styles MUST reference these variables.

```scss
// Colors
$primary-color: #7B61FF;    // Figma Purple
$bg-color: #F8F9FE;         // Page background
$text-main: #1A1D1E;        // Dark primary text
$text-sub: #6A6A6A;         // Muted secondary text

// Radii
$border-radius-lg: 48rpx;   // Card/Header (24px)
$border-radius-md: 24rpx;   // Buttons/Tags (12px)

// Glassmorphism
$glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
$glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
$glass-blur: 10px;
```

## 2. Component Architecture

### DuxCard (Base Container)
- **File**: `src/components/DuxCard/index.tsx`
- **Pattern**: Must use `$border-radius-lg` and `$card-shadow`.
- **Constraint**: No hardcoded widths; use Flexbox/Grid for responsiveness.

### DuxGrid (Layout)
- **File**: `src/components/DuxGrid/index.tsx`
- **Pattern**: Standard 2-column layout for products. Gap must be `24rpx` or `32rpx`.

## 3. Visual Patterns

### Glassmorphism (Glass Header)
When creating asset cards (like the Points card), use this pattern:
```scss
.glass-container {
  background: $glass-bg;
  backdrop-filter: blur($glass-blur);
  border: 1px solid $glass-border;
  border-radius: $border-radius-lg;
}
```

### Typography Hierarchy
- **Heading**: `font-weight: 800; font-size: 40rpx;`
- **Body**: `font-weight: 500; font-size: 28rpx; color: $text-main;`
- **Caption**: `font-weight: 400; font-size: 22rpx; color: rgba($text-white, 0.7);`

## 4. Asset Management
- **Icons**: Use `src/utils/assets.ts` -> `getIconifyUrl()`.
- **Scaling**: All interactive elements (cards/buttons) MUST have `:active { transform: scale(0.96); }`.
